00:36:09,410 --> 00:36:09,910
along with Lin Ge

590
00:36:09,910 --> 00:36:10,740
are pressurizing you.

591
00:36:11,750 --> 00:36:12,520
What are you going to do now?

592
00:36:12,830 --> 00:36:13,310
Don't worry.

593
00:36:13,800 --> 00:36:15,080
Different emperors
have different ministers.

594
00:36:15,160 --> 00:36:16,180
I'm prepared for this.

595
00:36:16,310 --> 00:36:17,040
I've looked out

596
00:36:17,080 --> 00:36:17,920
for good doctors before.

597
00:36:18,080 --> 00:36:18,960
I just need to recruit new people.

598
00:36:19,120 --> 00:36:19,810
But Lin Ge

599
00:36:19,860 --> 00:36:21,150
has a lot of VIP clients.

600
00:36:21,150 --> 00:36:21,920
So what?

601
00:36:22,560 --> 00:36:23,150
Every hospital

602
00:36:23,190 --> 00:36:24,230
has its own niche.

603
00:36:24,560 --> 00:36:25,600
Since Mr. Pan retired,

604
00:36:26,150 --> 00:36:27,400
Haicheng Hospital's orthopedics department
has been going down.

605
00:36:27,670 --> 00:36:28,350
It's because it

606
00:36:28,400 --> 00:36:29,480
doesn't have the unique skills anymore.

607
00:36:30,080 --> 00:36:30,760
But now,

608
00:36:30,790 --> 00:36:32,210
We have
late liver intervention embolization,

609
00:36:32,270 --> 00:36:32,600
as well

610
00:36:32,600 --> 00:36:32,960
as TIPS.

611
00:36:33,040 --> 00:36:33,830
From now on, Haicheng Hospital

612
00:36:34,150 --> 00:36:35,720
is going to be known
for its famous doctors.

613
00:36:35,920 --> 00:36:37,120
Does Zheng Ren give you confidence?

614
00:36:38,440 --> 00:36:38,870
Yes.

615
00:36:39,440 --> 00:36:40,930
That's why

616
00:36:40,930 --> 00:36:41,920
