- No need.

621
00:37:15,710 --> 00:37:16,480
Just stall for a while.

622
00:37:18,190 --> 00:37:18,670
Stall?

623
00:37:19,150 --> 00:37:20,400
They quit a little early.

624
00:37:20,870 --> 00:37:21,670
I haven't found

625
00:37:21,710 --> 00:37:22,400
other candidates yet.

626
00:37:22,560 --> 00:37:23,000
So,

627
00:37:23,640 --> 00:37:24,350
stall for a while.

628
00:37:35,270 --> 00:37:36,560
You want to fire them all?

629
00:37:39,520 --> 00:37:40,870
That's not what I had in mind.

630
00:37:41,960 --> 00:37:42,830
I've racked my brain

631
00:37:42,920 --> 00:37:44,640
and referenced national
and international success stories

632
00:37:45,600 --> 00:37:47,350
to make them competitive

633
00:37:47,640 --> 00:37:48,830
instead of relying on their past credits

634
00:37:48,920 --> 00:37:49,870
and waiting to retire.

635
00:37:50,150 --> 00:37:51,230
This is the age

636
00:37:51,270 --> 00:37:52,270
of transparent information
about applications.

637
00:37:52,830 --> 00:37:54,230
If we don't keep up with the times

638
00:37:54,560 --> 00:37:55,790
or make changes,

639
00:37:55,960 --> 00:37:57,310
we are doomed to be out.

640
00:38:00,040 --> 00:38:01,270
You're right.

641
00:38:02,040 --> 00:38:02,670
So

642
00:38:03,960 --> 00:38:05,440
I gave them a chance,

643
00:38:06,950 --> 00:38:08,520
but they didn't appreciate it

644
00:38:09,960 --> 00:38:11,830
and questioned my training of Zheng Ren.

645
00:38:14,080 --> 00:38:15,810
Is Zheng Ren the one
they want to get rid of?

646
00:38:20,670 --> 00:38:21,230
No.

647
00:38:22,600 --> 00:38:23,230
It's me.

648
00:38:28,640 --> 00:38:29,560
You still

649
00:38:30,830 --> 00:38:31,920
won't give up on the hospital?

650
00:38:33,040 --> 00:38:33,680
I'm not someone

651
00:38:33,680 --> 00:38:34,750
who runs away from things.

652
00:38:40,750 --> 00:38:42,440
From the day I decided to reform,

653
00:38:43,670 --> 00:38:44,230
I knew

654
00:38:44,230 --> 00:38:45,670
these old staff would cause trouble.

655
00:38:46,190 --> 00:38:47,440
I trained Zheng Ren

656
00:38:47,830 --> 00:38:49,190
and fully supported
the Interventional Department

657
00:38:49,710 --> 00:38:51,190
for this day.

658
00:38:51,670 --> 00:38:53,270
As long as Zheng Ren is here,

659
00:38:54,150 --> 00:38:55,350
I'm not afraid of them making trouble

660
00:38:56,080 --> 00:38:57,310
or leaving.

661
00:38:59,120 --> 00:38:59,670
Speaking of which,

662
00:39:00,270 --> 00:39:01,150
I'd like to thank you

663
00:39:02,870 --> 00:39:03,600
for giving me

664
00:39:03,640 --> 00:39:04,520
such a good student.

665
00:39:15,870 --> 00:39:16,440
Hua.

666
